data.description: Check out this spacious home located outside of the city limits in Pineville. This 3 bed 2 bath home offers almost 2100 heated square feet of living space with TWO fireplaces and large bedrooms. This home features an oversized sunroom that could easily be converted to a bedroom and a separate living space/bonus room separate from the main house with its own half bath.  Most of the major components have been updated to include: A new roof installed in 2020, the inside and outside HVAC units were replaced in 2021, and the water heater is only a year old. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your home!
